'''滿族人名'''是指[[满族|满族]]人的[[姓名|姓名]]。从[[女真|女真]]时代至现代，经历了数百年间的巨变。

== 名字来源 ==
=== 个人名 ===
满人在传统上使用满语人名。[[满语|满语]]人名可能因年代久远，大多数都难以找到定义。一些学者试图对其进行分类。{{link-en|埃里希·海尼士|Erich Haenisch}}它们划分成十六类包括动物、植物、品质等。清史学者陈接先将满族人名划分为七个主要类别<ref name=Stary>{{Cite journal|author=Giovanni Stary|title=Manchu names and some problems concerning their transcription|url=https://journal.fi/store/article/view/45165|language=en|journal=Studia Orientalia Electronica|volume=87|pages=245-252|date=2014-05-09|access-date=2019-01-10|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909121107/https://journal.fi/store/article/view/45165|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{rp|245}}。满人也有使用数字做名字的{{r|Elliott2001|page=243}}：常得自其诞生时父亲或祖父的年龄{{r|庄}}。如[[那丹珠|那丹珠]]（七十）、[[乌云珠|乌云珠]]（九十），或用汉语，如[[六十七_(鑲紅旗)|六十七]]、[[七十五_(将军)|七十五]]等{{r|Stary}}。表示品质的名字有的以-ngga/-ngge/-nggo结尾，也可以使用蒙古语后缀-tai/-tu结尾{{r|Elliott2001|page=243}}。以“Songgotu”为例，在[[满语|满语]]中，songgo为“哭”的词根<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20180912/20180912A1M30H00 |title=从《如懿传》里富察皇后家族看清朝人命名的那些事 |accessdate=2019-07-05 |author= |date=2018-09-14 |work= |publisher=腾讯网 |language=Zh-hans |archive-date=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716014441/https://new.qq.com/omn/20180912/20180912A1M30H00 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Songgotu之意，即为好哭。

尼堪（Nikan，意思是“汉人”）是一个后金时期常见的满族名字。<ref name="Elliott2001">{{cite book|author=Mark C. Elliott|title=The Manchu Way: The Eight Banners and Ethnic Identity in Late Imperial China|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_qtgoTIAiKUC&pg=PA242#v=onepage&q&f=false|year=2001|publisher=Stanford University Press|isbn=978-0-8047-4684-7|pages=242–}}</ref>[[尼堪外兰|尼堪外兰]]是一个[[女真|女真]]首领，与努尔哈赤敌对。<ref name="Crossley2000">{{cite book|author=Pamela Kyle Crossley|title=A Translucent Mirror: History and Identity in Qing Imperial Ideology|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Wn4iv_RJv8oC&pg=PA172&dq=nikan+wailan+chinese+official&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi3ufzku_jMAhXD4D4KHXnODR8Q6AEIHTAA#v=onepage&q=nikan%20wailan%20chinese%20official&f=false|date=15 February 2000|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-92884-8|pages=172–}}</ref><ref name="JR.1985">{{cite book|author=FREDERIC WAKEMAN JR.|title=The Great Enterprise: The Manchu Reconstruction of Imperial Order in Seventeenth-century China|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8nXLwSG2O8AC&pg=PA49&dq=nikan+wailan+chinese+official&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi3ufzku_jMAhXD4D4KHXnODR8Q6AEIIzAB#v=onepage&q=nikan%20wailan%20chinese%20official&f=false|year=1985|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-04804-1}}</ref>{{rp|49}}努尔哈赤的孙子中也有一个名叫[[尼堪_(清朝宗室)|尼堪]]的亲王，乃是废太子[[褚英|褚英]]之子，是[[多尔衮|多尔衮]]的支持者。<ref name="Rawski1998 2">{{cite book|author=Evelyn S. Rawski|title=The Last Emperors: A Social History of Qing Imperial Institutions|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5iN5J9G76h0C&pg=PA99&dq=nikan+mandahai&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwicrP7tu_jMAhXHyT4KHUWcCzgQ6AEIHTAA#v=onepage&q=nikan%20mandahai&f=false|date=15 November 1998|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-92679-0|pages=99–}}</ref>{{r|JR.1985|page1=902}}

